I love you more than words can say. Every single day, forever and a day.
Happy Anniversary

Description:
This anniversary card features a big gold heart in the background, slightly faded, with "6 months" written on top of the card and "Happy Anniversary" at the bottom. Two loving stick figure people are holding 2 red heart intertwined balloons to celebrate the occasion. The card also displays the exact years, months, days, hours, and minutes the couple have been together, making it a perfect way to commemorate their 6 month anniversary.
